casebody.data:
William David BURNSIDE, petitioner,
v.
T. WALTERS, et al. No. 12-7892. Supreme Court of the United States June 3, 2013.

Motion of petitioner to remand granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit for further consideration in light of LaFountain v. Harry, No. 11-1496, 2013 WL 2221569 (C.A.6, May 22, 2013).
